social_posts.post_text:
10 years true love mawage 
Two rings 
On two separate hands

Uncorked these 2014 vintage, estate grown  @nikesb Janoski’s. Smooth yet complex with subtle notes of switch crooked grinds and 360 flips. Pairs nicely with this @habitatskateboards cork top cruiser. 🎥 @junktown

@stefanjanoski in #nothingbutthetruth with @leeperskateschool and brandonbiebel 💎✨ @nikesb #2007 @danwolfe @joey_digital @chris_middlebrook @heyfilmthis 📼✨ #stefanjanoski #memoryscreen // drop a comment if you know who filmed
Who needs a DVD player when you can watch @stefanjanoski’s 2007 video part from Inhabitants on Instagram. 🍿
Stefan still skates, he’ll show you the way at 10am on STORIED Skateboarding Youtube 💪 “I Used To Skate” with @stefanjanoski & @guymariano - Signed boards available now at storiedskateboarding

“I Used To Skate” is live now on STORIED Skateboarding!  Starring Stefan Janoski & Guy Mariano. Be sure to check out the full video.  By the way, did you catch the cameos by @authenticandyanderson & @kellyhart ?! @stefanjanoski @guymariano
